      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, boil a kettle</p><p>Chop your <strong>waxy potatoes</strong> into large, bite-sized pieces</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped potatoes</strong> to a pot with plenty of <strong>boiled water </strong>and a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium and cook for 12-15 min or until fork-tender</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
