            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pan to a medium heat with your <strong>curry powder </strong>and cook for 2 min or until fragrant</p><p>Tip: Add a drizzle of oil if your pan is looking a little dry!</p><p>Once fragrant, remove the pan from the heat and add the <strong>drained potatoes</strong> with your<strong> white wine vinegar</strong>,<strong> mayo</strong>, <strong>sliced shallot</strong> and most of the <strong>chopped herbs</strong> (save some for garnish!)</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1595258389100-x200.jpg",
