    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> crispy chicken</strong> with the<strong> curried potato salad </strong>and <strong>green beans & peas </strong>to the side</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>reserved chopped herbs </strong>and <strong>nigella seeds</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
